                    <span>This book pointed out many useful tactics that cost you little to carry out.  It is very practical as we can see many successful cases.  Every one knows that cost incurred in marketing is so high that it narrow our margins and make us unable to offer competitive price.  Using the strategies in this book is going to save you a lot.  It included other useful information such as how to build up a professional image and how to establish the strategic alliance.  If you want to increase your competitiveness of your product, you have to read this book.</span>
                  
              
